    "description": "Copyright © 2021 Kimi-Arthur\nclean        Clean file entries.\nrm           Remove the FILE. Can be either logic path like: /Software/... or\nreal path like: local:desk/Software....\ncp           Copy FILE1 to FILE2. The files will be linked.\nls           List files and folders in the FOLDER.\nupload       Upload file to a cloud location.\nadd          Add file entry.\nget          Get files.\ntouch        Touch file.\nnormalize    Rename the file with proper normalization.\nimport       Import files from /Downloads folder with resource id.\ntrash        Move the file to trash.\nrm-empty     Remove empty folders recursively.\ndecode       Decode file.\ndedup        Deduplicate file entries.\nmigrate      Migrate Google Drive files to a new cell and quick check on it.\nlink         Link $ folders to create proper directory structure.\nextract      Extract files and add to system.\ntruncate     Special command to truncate the last byte of the files in case it\nends with \\0.\nhelp         Display more information on a specific command.\nversion      Display version information."
  },
